cle by Moraes, Ribeiro and Correa. In addition, we quote that the solutions\nobtained by Velten and Caram\\^es are unfeasible in view of their mathematical\nmisunderstanding.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 20:13:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Sep 2017 18:22:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-22"}
