clude the Nash equilibrium of the original potential game. We\ndemonstrate the validity of our approximation method through two numerical\nexamples on simplified weather forecasting and multi-target tracking.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Jul 2017 01:47:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-05"}
